@startuml heterogeneity_matrix
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 8

title **Agent Heterogeneity — Multi-Model Architecture**

skinparam object {
  BackgroundColor #FAFAFA
  BorderColor #BDBDBD
  FontColor #1A1A1A
}

object "**Engagement Manager**" as em #E3F2FD {
  Model = qwen3:8b (Small)
  Provider = Ollama (local)
  Tools = none
  Output = Analysis Plan JSON
  Role = Task decomposition
  Reasoning = /no_think mode, fast structured task
}

object "**Market Researcher**" as mr #E8F5E9 {
  Model = qwen3:14b (Medium)
  Provider = Ollama (local)
  Tools = search_web(), read_document()
  Output = Market Analysis JSON
  Role = Market investigation
  Reasoning = /think mode, synthesis ability
}

object "**Financial Analyst**" as fa #FFF3E0 {
  Model = deepseek-r1:14b (L3) / qwen3:14b (L4)
  Provider = Ollama (local)
  Tools = none (pure analysis from context)
  Output = Financial Analysis JSON
  Role = Quantitative analysis
  Reasoning = Chain-of-thought / /think mode
}

object "**Risk Analyst**" as ra #FFEBEE {
  Model = qwen3:14b (Medium)
  Provider = Ollama (local)
  Tools = search_web(), read_document(), assess_risk()
  Output = Risk Matrix JSON
  Role = Risk identification
  Reasoning = /think mode, edge case thinking
}

object "**Strategy Consultant**" as sc #F3E5F5 {
  Model = qwen3:32b (L3) / qwen3.5:27b (L4)
  Provider = Ollama (local)
  Tools = reads all analyses from context
  Output = Consulting Report JSON
  Role = Synthesis & recommendation
  Reasoning = /think mode, best writing & reasoning
}

object "**Evaluator** (L4 only)" as ev #FFFDE7 {
  Model = Claude Opus 4.6 (Large)
  Provider = Anthropic API (cloud)
  Tools = reads report from context
  Output = Scorecard JSON
  Role = Independent quality judge
  Reasoning = Critical assessment
}

em -[hidden]right- mr
mr -[hidden]right- fa
fa -[hidden]down- ra
ra -[hidden]left- sc
sc -[hidden]left- ev

note as N1
  **Heterogeneity Dimensions:**
  1. **Model Size:** 8B → 14B → 27B/32B
  2. **Model Family:** Qwen 3, Qwen 3.5, DeepSeek R1, Claude
  3. **Provider:** Ollama (local) + Anthropic API (evaluator)
  4. **Tools:** Different tool sets per agent
  5. **Reasoning:** /think vs /no_think modes, chain-of-thought control
end note

@enduml
